<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>I have done this quest at least 3 times, there is no running around Freeport and questing. All you have to do is: <br />1. enter befallen <br />2. kill all excavating skellies <br />3. wait for them to respawn and kill them again <br />4. repeat until the foreman spawns <br />5. kill foreman and sir ariam spawns <br />6. tell him &quot;I sense the burning dead&quot; <br />7. he gives you the bridle <br /> <br />there ya go, have fun with your horsie! ive had n00bs ask about the quest and ill tell them...for a price&gt;:-&gt; <br /> <br />Medya Wyvernslayer <br />44 magician of Quellious <br />Bertoxxulous server <br />P.S.- the horse is white, with black mane and hooves, pinkish muzzle <br /> <br /> <br /><em class="fs8">Edited, Wed Jan 22 16:53:47 2003</em></p>
