<td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>The only items I'm aware of that can be recharged are some of the tinkered items, and then only a few of those, and they all use a mana battery to be made, and to be recharged. And to name names on those, Anizok's Gauze press and Min / Max devices, Gnomish Vanishing Device, and the Clockwork Watchman armors. <br /> <br /> <br />On the topic of the horse itself, I'd have to say if you're a caster and doing a planar raid, do this quest, it's well worth being able to meditate, even while casting (I've done some long cast spells and mana still regens at the same rate) And I say especially for Fear raids, since if you're on a break group, you can't sit down initially for the sake of avoiding extra aggros. <br /> <br /><em class="fs8">Edited, Thu Dec  5 14:23:03 2002</em></p>
